results.name: Numbers n such that continued fraction for sqrt(n) has period 67.
mathematica: cf67Q[n_]:=Module[{s=Sqrt[n]},If[IntegerQ[s],1,Length[ ContinuedFraction[ s][[2]]]]==67]; Select[Range[33000],cf67Q] (* _Harvey P. Dale_, Sep 21 2018 *)
